===Format===
'''BGIS: 2023 The Grind:'''''  July 20th - August 20th, 2023

Maps: {{Abbr/TPP}} [[Erangel]], [[Miramar]] and [[Sanhok]]
* '''''Round 1 Week 1:'''  July 20th - 23rd, 2023''
** '''128 Invited Teams'''
** Teams divided into 8 groups with 16 squads in each group.
** Each team will play to total of 3 games.
** {{Bgcolortext|up|''Top 8 teams from each group}} advance to '''''Week-3''''' 
** {{Bgcolortext|up|''64 teams}} overall advance to '''''Week-3''''' 

* '''''Round 1 Week 2:'''  July 27th - 30th, 2023''
** '''128 Invited Teams'''
** Teams divided into 8 groups with 16 squads in each group.
** Each team will play to total of 3 games.
** {{Bgcolortext|up|''Top 8 teams from each group advance to}} '''''Week-4''''' 
** {{Bgcolortext|up|''64 teams}} overall advance to '''''Week-4''''' ''

* '''''Round 2 Week 1:'''  August 3rd - 6th, 2023
** '''''64 Teams'''''
** 64 teams from ''Week-1'' will be divided into 4 groups.
** Each group will play a total of 6 matches.
** {{Bgcolortext|up|''Top 8  teams from each group}} will qualify for the '''''Round-3'''''

* '''''Round 2 Week 2:'''  August 10th - 13th, 2023
** '''''64 Teams'''''
** 64 teams from ''Week-2'' will be divided into 4 groups.
** Each group will play a total of 6 matches.
** {{Bgcolortext|up|''Top 8  teams from each group}} will qualify for the '''''Round-3'''''

* '''Round 3:'''  August 17th - 20th, 2023
** '''''64 Teams'''''
**  32 teams from '''Round 2 Week-1''' + 32 teams from '''Round 2 Week-2''' will compete in a round robin format

===Allocations===
* {{Bgcolortext|up|'''''Top 32 teams'''''}} qualify for '''[https://liquipedia.net/pubgmobile/Battlegrounds_Mobile_India_Series/2023/ BGIS 2023: Main Event Round 3]'''
* {{Bgcolortext|stayup|'''''Bottom 32 teams'''''}} qualify for '''[https://liquipedia.net/pubgmobile/Battlegrounds_Mobile_India_Series/2023/ BGIS 2023: Main Event Round 2]'''

