===Format===
* '''League Stage:''''' Feb 16th - Apr 6th, 2025
**{{TextDropdown|title=For League Stage format|section=LeagueStage|width=max-content}}
* '''Round 1:''''' Feb 16th - 23th, 2025
** 1024 Teams, 8 matchdays.
*** {{Bgcolortext|stayup|1016 Teams}} from In-Game Qualifiers.
*** {{Bgcolortext|stayup|Bottom 8 Teams}} from The Grind Week-1.
** Teams divided into 64 groups with 16 Teams in each group.
** Each team plays a total of 6 matches.
** {{bgcolortext|up|Top 7 Teams}} from each group + {{bgcolortext|up|Top 48 Teams}} among the remaining teams (Total 496 Teams) qualify for ''Round 2.

* '''Round 2:''''' Feb 27th - Mar 2nd, 2025
** 512 Teams, 4 matchdays.
*** {{Bgcolortext|stayup|496 Teams}} from Round 1.
*** {{Bgcolortext|stayup|Top 8 Teams}} from The Grind Week-1.
*** {{Bgcolortext|stayup|Bottom 8 Teams}} from The Grind Week-2.
** Teams are divided into 32 groups with 16 Teams in each group.
** Each team plays a total of 6 matches.
** {{bgcolortext|up|Top 7 Teams}} from each group + {{bgcolortext|up|Top 16 Teams}} among the remaining teams (Total 240 Teams) qualify for ''Round 3.

* '''Round 3:''''' Mar 6th - 9th, 2025
** 256 Teams, 4 matchdays.
*** {{Bgcolortext|stayup|240 Teams}} from Round 2.
*** {{Bgcolortext|stayup|Top 8 Teams}} from The Grind Week-2.
*** {{Bgcolortext|stayup|Bottom 8 Teams}} from The Grind Week-3.
** Teams are divided into 16 groups with 16 Teams in each group.
** Each team plays a total of 6 matches.
** {{bgcolortext|up|Top 6 Teams}} from each group + {{bgcolortext|up|Top 16 Teams}} among the remaining teams (Total 112 Teams) qualify for ''Round 4.

* '''Round 4:''''' <!--Mar 13rd - 16th--> Mar 11th , 12th , 15th & 16th, 2025
** 128 Teams, 4 matchdays.
*** {{Bgcolortext|stayup|112 Teams}} from Round 3.
*** {{Bgcolortext|stayup|Top 8 Teams}} from The Grind Week-3.
*** {{Bgcolortext|stayup|Bottom 8 Teams}} from The Grind Week-4.
** Teams are divided into 8 groups with 16 Teams in each group.
** Each team plays a total of 6 matches.
** {{bgcolortext|up|Top 7 Teams}} from each group (Total 56 Teams) advance to ''Quarter Finals.
** {{bgcolortext|stay|Top 16 Teams}} among the remaining teams advance to ''Wildcard.

* '''Quarter Finals:''''' Mar 20th - 23th, 2025
** 64 Teams, 4 matchdays.
*** {{Bgcolortext|stayup|56 Teams}} from Round 4.
*** {{Bgcolortext|stayup|Top 8 Teams}} from The Grind Week-4.
** Teams are divided into 4 groups with 16 Teams in each group.
** Each team plays a total of 6 matches.
** {{bgcolortext|up|Top 16 Teams}} based on the cumulative overall standings advance to the ''Semi Finals Week 1.
** {{bgcolortext|stay|Remaining 48 Teams}} advance to the ''Wildcard.

* '''Wildcard:''''' Mar 24th - 27th, 2025
** 64 Teams, 4 matchdays.
*** {{Bgcolortext|stayup|48 Teams}} from Quarter Finals.
*** {{Bgcolortext|stayup|16 Teams}} from Round 4.
** Teams are divided into 4 groups with 16 Teams in each group.
** Each team plays 3 matches over 2 days.
** After 2 days, based on the overall standings teams are re-shuffled.
** Again, each team plays 3 matches for 2 days.
** {{bgcolortext|up|Top 16 Teams}} based on the cumulative overall standings advance to the ''Semi Finals Week 1  .

* '''Semi Finals Week 1:''''' Mar 29th - 30th & Apr 1st - 2nd, 2025
** 32 Teams, 4 matchdays.
*** {{Bgcolortext|stayup|16 Teams}} from Quarter Finals.
*** {{Bgcolortext|stayup|16 Teams}} from Wildcard.
** Teams are divided into 4 groups with 8 Teams in each group.
** Round-robin format.
** Each team plays a total of 12 matches.
** {{bgcolortext|up|Top 8 Teams}} advance to the ''Grand Finals.
** {{bgcolortext|stay|Remaining 24 Teams}} proceed to ''Semi Finals Week 2.

* '''Semi Finals Week 2:''''' Apr 3rd - 6th, 2025
** 24 Teams, 4 matchdays.
** Teams are divided equally into 3 groups of 8.
** Double Round-robin format.
** Each team plays a total of 16 matches.
** {{bgcolortext|up|Top 8 Teams}} advance to the ''Grand Finals''.
{{TextDropdown|end}}

* '''The Grand Finals:''''' Apr 25th - 27th, 2025 at Biswa Bangla Mela Prangan {{Flag|in}} Kolkata.
** 16 Teams, 3 matchdays.
*** {{Bgcolortext|stayup|8 teams}} from Semi Finals Week 1.
*** {{Bgcolortext|stayup|8 teams}} from Semi Finals Week 2.
** 18 matches (6 each day).

