'''Battlegrounds Mobile India Pro Series 2025''' or '''BMPS 2025''' is the fourth edition of ''[[Battlegrounds Mobile India Pro Series|Battlegrounds Mobile India Pro Series]]''.

==About==
===Format===
* '''League Stage:''''' May 22nd - June 22nd, 2025
** 96 teams.
** Squad, {{Abbr/TPP}}
**{{TextDropdown|title=For League Stage format|section=LeagueStage|width=max-content}}
* '''Round 1:''''' May 22nd - June 3rd, 2025
** 96 teams, 12 matchdays.
** Teams are divided into 6 groups of 16 teams each.
** Each group plays 3 matches for 3 days (total 12 matches).
** Groups are reshuffled after each 3 days.
** {{bgcolortext|up|Top 8 teams}} from the overall standings qualify for ''Semi Finals Week 1.
** {{bgcolortext|stayup|9th - 16th}} from the overall standings qualify for ''Round 3.
** {{bgcolortext|stay|Top 64 teams}} from the overall standings (except 1st - 16th ranked) advance to ''Round 2.
** {{bgcolortext|down|16 teams}} are eliminated.

* '''Round 2:''''' June 5th - June 8th, 2025
** 64 teams, 4 matchdays.
** Teams are divided into 4 groups of 16 teams each.
** Each group plays 6 matches.
** {{bgcolortext|up|Top 40 teams}} from the overall standings qualify for ''Round 3.

* '''Round 3:''''' June 9th - June 12th, 2025
** 48 teams, 4 matchdays.
*** 8 teams from Round 1.
*** 40 teams from Round 2.
** Teams are divided into 3 groups of 16 teams each.
** Groups are reshuffled after 2 days.
** Each team plays a total of 8 matches.
** {{bgcolortext|up|Top 24 teams}} from the overall standings qualify for ''Semi Finals Week 1.

* '''Semi Finals Week 1:''''' June 14th - June 17th, 2025
** 32 teams, 4 matchdays.
*** 8 teams from Round 1.
*** 24 teams from Round 3.
** Teams are divided into 4 groups of 8 teams each.
** Round-robin format.
** Each team plays a total of 12 matches (3/day).
** {{bgcolortext|up|Top 8 teams}} from the overall standings qualify for ''Grand Finals.
** {{bgcolortext|stayup|Remaining 24 teams}} advance to ''Semi Finals Week 2.

* '''Semi Finals Week 2:''''' June 19th - June 22nd, 2025
** 24 teams, 4 matchdays.
** Teams are divided into 3 groups of 8 teams each.
** Double Round-robin format.
** Each team plays a total of 16 matches (4/day).
** {{bgcolortext|up|Top 8 teams}} from the overall standings qualify for ''Grand Finals.{{TextDropdown|end}}
<div style=margin-top:10px></div>
* '''Grand Finals:''''' July 4th - July 6th, 2025 at Yashobhoomi Convention Centre, {{Flag|in}} Delhi.
** 16 teams, 3 matchdays.
*** 8 teams from Semi Finals 1.
*** 8 teams from Semi Finals 2.
** 18 matches (6 each day).

